| Disable Break & Escape keys, switch NumLock off, standby reboots
FX 229 1
FX 247 170
FX 202 4 251
FX 118
STBState_Reboot 1
STBStateOn
Hon
Set STBSplash$Disable Y

| Change mode, define text window and switch off cursor
Echo |L|\|EBN|D|W|A|@|@|@|@|@|@|@|@

| The root of the run-time directory (if any)
|Set NetRoot$Dir  NFS::NFSBoot.$
|Set NetRoot$Dir  LanMan::ARMBoot.$
Set NetRoot$Path <NetRoot$Dir>.

| The root of the boot-time directory
Set STBRoot$Dir  Resources:$.STB
Set STBRoot$Path <STBRoot$Dir>.

| This path is needed until we have established what is local
Set Root$Path <STBRoot$Path>,<NetRoot$Path>

| Display an initial splash screen
STBSplash_Graphic Resources:$.Resources.STBSplash.Screen
STBSplash_Display ««TFTPBoot»»

| Mount the run-time directory (if required)
|NFS:Mount -host 136.170.32.3 NFSBoot /stbboot/live/TFTP
|LanMan:LMConnect ARMBoot 136.170.38.221 ARMBoot

| Download the Baseline archive
TFTPLoadModule <Inet$BootServer> ArcTFTP,ffa

| Start the main boot application
/Root:!STBBoot
